MESSAGE Simple mail
BODY BEGIN
From: gray@gnu.org
To: bug-mailutils@gnu.org
Subject: Simple mail

This is a simple mail.
Data goes here.
BODY END

PATTERN BEGIN
ENVELOPE FROM: <gray@gnu.org>
ENVELOPE TO: <bug-mailutils@gnu.org>
   0: From: gray@gnu.org
   1: To: bug-mailutils@gnu.org
   2: Subject: Simple mail
   3:
   4: This is a simple mail.
   5: Data goes here.
   6:
END OF MESSAGE
PATTERN END
MESSAGE END

