   0: From: gray@gnu.org
   1: To: bug-mailutils@gnu.org
   2: Cc: alainm@gnu.org
   3: Subject: Carbon copy test
   4:
   5: CC works.
   6:
END OF MESSAGE
PATTERN END
MESSAGE END

